                        "displayName": "Joris Van den Bossche",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Europe/Brussels"
                    },
                    "body": "This is known issue with wheels of older versions, see the linked issue and https://github.com/numpy/numpy/issues/17913. This is fixed in the latest {{pyarrow}} 3.0.0 release, so please update your {{pyarrow}} version if you want to use the latest NumPy release.",
